      "id": "uhA_secd",
      "x": 82,
      "y": 1158,
      "width": 600,
      "height": 34,
      "text": "the request can't block on a card settling, so it returns optimistically.\nSquare confirms out-of-band with a SIGNED webhook the async tier reconciles.",
